HEADWORD: Refar
<hw>Re*far"</hw> <pr>(r?*f?r")</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>refaire</ets> to do over again.]</ety> <def>To go over again; to
repeat.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>To him therefore this wonder done <qex>refar</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Fairfax.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

